 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">For a neat, streamlined hall, you can always rely on modular showcase designs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Settle For Perfect: Best Showcase Design For Hall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For small halls, it makes sense to have a functional yet chic showcase design, right? Take a look at this sleek showcase and take inspiration. With smartly placed shelves for books, cabinets for valuables and a seamless space for decor knick-knacks, this is one of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-showcase-designs\/\">best showcase designs for your living room<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005731\/best-showcase-design-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Simple showcase designs for small hall by placed shelves for books, cabinets\" class=\"wp-image-5959\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005731\/best-showcase-design-hall.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005731\/best-showcase-design-hall-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005731\/best-showcase-design-hall-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005731\/best-showcase-design-hall-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The best showcase design for your living area is the one that takes less space yet smartly houses everything<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Do It The Desi Way: Indian Style Showcase Designs For Hall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A showcase design looks incomplete without embellishments. So why not give your hall an Indian touch with this simple showcase design. It is designed with an engraved cabinet and floating shelves. For small and minimalistic rooms, this Indian style showcase design is absolutely on point.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005735\/indian-style-showcase-designs-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Indian houses with simple showcase designs for hall\" class=\"wp-image-5960\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005735\/indian-style-showcase-designs-hall.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005735\/indian-style-showcase-designs-hall-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005735\/indian-style-showcase-designs-hall-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005735\/indian-style-showcase-designs-hall-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A neatly engraved showcase design is ideal for modern yet Indian homes<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Keep It Stylish: A Modern Showcase Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A modern home deserves a showcase design that is functional and aesthetic. Choose this design as it makes smart use of vertical space. It also uses wall space on either side to its fullest and you can display souvenirs, knick-knacks, frames on this showcase.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005739\/modern-showcase-design-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Small use of vertical space to make a modern simple showcase designs for hall\" class=\"wp-image-5961\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005739\/modern-showcase-design-hall.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005739\/modern-showca