ps:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005742\/simple-glass-showcase-designs-hall-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Choose a showcase design that makes smart use of its glass elements<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple TV Showcase Designs For Hall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This showcase design mainly revolves around your television set. With floating shelves and cabinets around the TV, this showcase is ideal for those looking for a minimalistic look for hall interiors. Also, this showcase design makes smart use of walls making it perfect for small living areas and studio apartments.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005746\/lcd-showcase-design-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Simple tv showcase designs for hall and studio apartments\" class=\"wp-image-5963\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005746\/lcd-showcase-design-hall.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005746\/lcd-showcase-design-hall-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005746\/lcd-showcase-design-hall-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005746\/lcd-showcase-design-hall-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">LCD showcase design is perfect when you want a sleek and neat TV area in your hall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/tv-showcase-designs\/\">15 Latest TV Showcase Designs For Home<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">In Vogue: Latest Showcase Designs For Halls<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A combination of modern aesthetics and modular convenience, this showcase de